Kefir Overnight Oats

10 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh ProteinLow Sugar

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastHealthyEasy

Description

A creamy, tangy delight packed with nutrients, perfect for a quick breakfast!

Ingredients

  • rolled oats: 1 cup
  • kefir: 1 cup
  • honey: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh berries (strawberries, blueberries, or raspberries): 1/2 cup
  • chia seeds: 2 tablespoons
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
